            What is Redux? When should you use it? And how can it benifit you? We will try
            to answer these questions as well as get a better appreciation of Redux.
          a(href="/react") create react create-react-app
          hr
          h5 #{time}
          h3 
            a(href="/nodejs") Creating a cool card flipping animation in CSS\React
          p. 
            Use react and css to create a flipping card animation when card is hovered over.
          a(href="/react") react 
          a(href="/htmlcss") css 
          a(href="/htmlcss") animation
          hr
          h5 #{time}
          h3 
            a(href="/nodejs") Making a pong style multiplayer paddle game in p5.js
          p. 
            Remember that old game pong back from the 70's-80's, This will be my attempt to
            try and recreate it using processing p5.js and HTML5.
          hr
          h5 #{time}
          h3 
            a(href="/nodejs") Rogue style RPG using p5js and HTML5
          p. 
            I've been a gamer for as long as I can remember but some of my fondest memories are of
            an old game called Rogue. We will dev into procedural generation and create our own random 
            dungeon! You can click here to see how I did this with python as well in my game Dungeon Romper.
          hr
